<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4612548>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 13. Parabopyrella cuspidata, n. sp., holotype female (CIEAL560301) (A–I): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Left maxilliped, external view. D. Palp of maxilliped, internal view. E. Left side of barbula. F. Left oostegite 1, external view. G. Left oostegite 1, internal view. H. Right pereopod 2. I. Right pereopod 6. Allotype male (CIEAL560302) (J–M): J. Dorsal view. K. Ventral view. L. Right antennae and antennule. M. Left pereopod 7. Scale: 2 mm (A, B); 0.5 mm (C, E–G); 0.25 mm (D, H–K); 0.15 mm (L, M)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4612548/files/figure.png" .

